parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended increase in ringtone volume while connected to Apple Carplay can cause a sudden, loud ring, which can startle the driver and potentially lead to an accident.
symptoms: The ringtone volume setting is adjusted unwillingly along with the call/media volume during a phone call
resulting in a loud ring when a new call is received.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the panoramic sunroof while driving can cause a safety hazard, potentially leading to injuries or accidents.
symptoms: The sunroof explodes or makes a continuous creaking sound while driving
which can be a sign of a manufacturing defect.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the vehicle to pass a NHTSA crash test raises concerns about the safety of the vehicle, potentially putting occupants at risk in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The vehicle did not pass a NHTSA crash test
which can indicate a design or manufacturing flaw.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to safety risks, inconvenience, and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle does not start
warning lights appear on the dash display
malfunction alerts
battery light is lit
some features of the car do not work
ignition is turned off and car is locked
requires a jump to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause frustration, distraction, and inconvenience to the driver.
symptoms: The main screen blanks out
infotainment system needs to be rebooted often
lane departure is unreliable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hatchback and sensor systems can cause inconvenience, safety risks, and potential accidents.
symptoms: Rear hatch intermittently doesn't close properly
alarm stays on
hatchback randomly opens when walking near the back of the vehicle
hatchback closes while putting groceries in the back.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the mirror and wiper systems can cause inconvenience and distraction to the driver.
symptoms: Driver-side mirror won't fold out after retraction
rear wiper goes off for no reason.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the climate control system can cause inconvenience and discomfort to the occupants.
symptoms: Air conditioner has lost function twice.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise and adaptive control systems can cause inconvenience, distraction, and potential safety risks.
symptoms: Cruise and adaptive control indicators cease to function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning trunk door can cause inconvenience, difficulty in accessing the trunk, and potentially lead to safety issues if the door opens unexpectedly while driving.
symptoms: The trunk door does not open or close properly
the trunk door is stuck in an open or closed position
the trunk door latch is faulty
the trunk door does not align properly
the trunk door has a loud noise or vibration when opening or closing.
